C. H. Davis, et al., Appellants, v. M. C. Davis, et al., as County Commissioners of Manatee County, Appellees. Appeal from a decree of the Circuit Court for the County of Manatee. Sparkman & Cartel’, and C. T. Curry, for Appellants; C. C. Whitaker, for Appellees.

Appeal dismissed on praecipe of counsel for Appellant.
